https://drive.google.com/file/d/1aQP-j0mlV_M38dMONWrI5sgl7PuVH_b3/view?usp=sharing

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Unzip 'Buurdhis-Sanctuary.zip'.
- Move the file 'DM-Buurdhis-WindowsNoEditor.pak' into:
      %PROGRAMFILES%\Epic Games\UnrealTournament\UnrealTournament\Content\Paks\
- Launch Unreal Tournament and create a new custom game.


